products.name: Holiday blend
products.description: We have created a special blend especially for the holidays. Enjoy a multifaceted balanced flavor with sweet undertones supported by herbal and maple notes in our limited edition STARBUCKS® Holiday Blend medium roasted coffee beans.

products.name: Cappuccino
products.description: This rich velvety coffee expertly combines 100% Arabica beans and milk under a rich froth.

products.name: Caffè Latte
products.description: In this delicate creamy drink, 100% Arabica beans are ideally combined with delicate milk under a layer of soft foam.

products.name: Espresso Roast
products.description: This rich coffee blend from Latin America and Asia has a sweet caramel flavor. It was the taste of this coffee that became the basis of our latte recipe.

products.name: Pike Place® Roast
products.description: Enjoy the balanced taste of coffee from Latin America with light notes of cocoa beans and roasted nuts aroma.
